title: 100% wholemeal bread
ingredients: ['420ml warm water (43 degrees C)', '4 tablespoons honey', '2 teaspoons instant yeast', '725g stone-ground wholemeal flour', '6 tablespoons vital wheat gluten', '1 tablespoon flax seeds', '1 tablespoon ground flax seed', '1 tablespoon rolled oats', '1 tablespoon sesame seeds', '1 tablespoon quinoa', '1 tablespoon sunflower seeds', '1 teaspoon salt', '2 tablespoons coconut oil, melted']
